(74, 'Nail Stickers, ETEREAUTY Nail Art Stickers Decals New DIY Nail Design 3D Sticker 30 Sheets', 32, 0, 2209136, 100, 8.99, 8.99, 1, '373', '\n        \n\n\n\n\n\n  \n    \n  \n\n\n        \n        \n     \n	       \n     \n\n     \n                              \n     \n       	       \n        \n        &lt;!-- show up to 2 reviews by default --&gt; \n        \n        	\n        	\n        		\n        			&lt;p&gt;The ETEREAUTY nail art stickers are a fun way to add style or character to your nails without much effort. It will only take few minutes to apply, yet the design will have gorgeous, spectacular nail art effects!&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;--Instructions for Application: &lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt; 1. First apply a coat of polish to your nails, using a dark color if you want to use light-colored decals, or a light color for dark decals.&lt;br&gt; 2.Remove a decal from its sheet with tweezers and lay it in place on your a nail, then press it down lightly.&lt;br&gt; 3.These are small decals, so you can use more than one on each nail to build up your own design. &lt;br&gt;4.When you\'re happy with the designs you\'ve put together, you can apply a clear top coat polish to make the decals more permanent. &lt;br&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;b&gt;A highlight of this collection is that some of the decals are 3D. These have their pattern or image raised up a little, so they look like embossed metal or enamel. &lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt; Order today and you\'ll be able to create some really fun and creative effects with your nails. What\'s more, you can easily get totally professional-looking results that all your friends will admire! This ETEREAUTY product is sold with a full money-back guarantee. If you\'re dissatisfied with your purchase for any reason, contact us for a replacement or refund.&lt;br&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;b&gt;PACKAGE INCLUDES: &lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt; 4 x Sheets of small image nail decals &lt;br&gt; 30 Sheets Nail Stickers\n				    	\n					&lt;/p&gt;\n        		\n        		\n        	\n        \n                \n        \n        \n      \n      \n    \n    \n\n     \n        ', 'https://www.amazon.com/dp/B073GPBVLV/', 'TIME SAVING, SUPER CONVENIENT: No more complex painting! With this self-adhesive design, literally it only takes few seconds per nail to create the beautiful nail art designs.<br />\nABUNDANT COLLECTION AVAILABLE: 30 sheets, each one with dozens of decals and several different designs.You\'ll be able to create unique nail art every day, for any occasion! In this collection there are designs with Christmas themes, hearts, snowflakes, geometric patterns and much more.<br />\nCREATIVE FUN 3D EFFECT:Many of the designs are raised up slightly from the surface of your nail, creating an especially eye-catching effect. You can mix-and-match these 3D decals with flat ones.<br />\nSATISFY DIFFERENT ALL NEED: There are also multicolor designs,black, white,multi-color and more; Others in reflective gold and silver. You can use black designs with a light polish undercoat, white with dark.<br />\nBUY WITH CONFIDENCE, NO HASSLE MONEY-BACK GUARANTEE: If you\'re not completely satisfied with your purchase for any reason, simply let us know and we will either replace it or refund your money, your choice!<br />\n', 1542334969, 2, '', '', '', 1, 1, 1, NULL, NULL, 1, 1),
