p&gt;\n    \n\n    \n    \n        &lt;p class=&quot;a-spacing-base&quot;&gt;\n            &lt;span class=&quot;a-text-bold&quot;&gt;One of these trimming tools is the forked-tipped tool you can see in the illustrations. &lt;/span&gt; \n\n        &lt;/p&gt;\n    \n\n    \n    \n        &lt;p class=&quot;a-spacing-base&quot;&gt;\n            This  tool is used by simply sliding the tip along the cuticle line of your  nail. The point where the two teeth of the fork come together is sharp,  so it will trim any raised cuticle down flush with your nail. \n\n        &lt;/p&gt;\n    \n\n    \n    \n        &lt;p class=&quot;a-spacing-base&quot;&gt;\n            With  this unique new tool your nail and skin are protected from the sharp  blade, so it\'s safer than other cuticle trimming tools. \n        &lt;/p&gt;\n    \n\n    \n    \n        &lt;p class=&quot;a-spacing-base&quot;&gt;\n             \n        &lt;/p&gt;\n    \n\n    \n    \n        &lt;p class=&quot;a-spacing-base&quot;&gt;\n            In  addition to cuticle care, these tools can be used for tasks such as  scraping off softened gel polish residue, prying off false nails, and  cleaning under fingernails. \n\n        &lt;/p&gt;\n    \n\n    \n    \n        &lt;p class=&quot;a-spacing-base&quot;&gt;\n            The tools are all surgical grade  stainless steel that won\'t tarnish, is easy to clean and will stay  sharp. Professional instructions are included with the kit. \n\n        &lt;/p&gt;\n    \n\n    \n    \n        &lt;p class=&quot;a-spacing-base&quot;&gt;\n            &lt;span class=&quot;a-text-bold&quot;&gt;Package includes: &lt;/span&gt; \n\n        &lt;/p&gt;\n    \n\n    \n    \n        &lt;p class=&quot;a-spacing-base&quot;&gt;\n            Five-piece cuticle pusher remover kit \n\n        &lt;/p&gt;\n    \n\n    \n    \n        &lt;p class=&quot;a-spacing-base&quot;&gt;\n            Metal storage case \n\n        &lt;/p&gt;\n    \n\n    \n    \n        &lt;p class=&quot;a-spacing-base&quot;&gt