(87, 'Nail Art Set, ETEREAUTY Nail Art Kit 15pcs Nail Art Brush, 30 Rolls of Striping Tape Gold Tweezer Gold and Silver Studs Decorations Nail Rhinestones Gold Nail Art Studs', 32, 0, 2173163, 100, 10.99, 10.99, 1, '388', '\n        \n\n\n\n\n\n  \n    \n       \n        \n          \n        &lt;div class=&quot;disclaim&quot;&gt;\n          \n            \n            \n            \n             Size:&lt;strong&gt;style 2&lt;/strong&gt;\n            \n          \n          &lt;/div&gt;\n        \n      \n    \n  \n\n\n        \n        \n     \n	       \n     \n\n     \n                              \n     \n       	       \n        \n        &lt;!-- show up to 2 reviews by default --&gt; \n        \n        	\n        	\n        		\n        			&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;With this set of tools and supplies, you\'ll have what you need to have fun and get creative as you decorate your nails. &lt;br&gt; Just add a range of colors of nail polish and you\'ll be ready to start expressing yourself!&lt;/b&gt; &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;For doing freehand artwork on your nails, you\'ll love the set of 15 brushes in this kit. &lt;/b&gt; &lt;br&gt;These are top-quality brushes, and they come in all the shapes and sizes you’ll need for all sorts of nail-decoration tasks and effects. &lt;br&gt; Most of the time you can just wipe the brush with a paper towel while the polish is still wet, and occasionally you\'ll want to clean them with nail polish remover or acetone. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Also in the kit is a full suite of 3D nail decorations, including rhinestones in 12 different colors and gold and silver studs. &lt;/b&gt; &lt;br&gt;These items come in three cleverly designed cases with rotating lids. &lt;br&gt; The lids only expose one small compartment at a time, so you never have to worry about accidentally spilling hundreds of tiny items all over your floor.&amp;nbsp; &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Next in the set is a selection of 30 different colors and widths of striping tape Which is the most popular forms of contemporary nail decoration. &lt;/b&gt; &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;And finally there\'s the pair of fine tweezers. &lt;/b&gt; &lt;br&gt;This tool is elegantly shaped and great to look at, and made with precision-ground angled tips that make it perfect for picking up and placing the tapes, studs, and rhinestones in this kit. &lt;br&gt;15 Nail art brushes &lt;br&gt;1 Box rhinestone decorations &lt;br&gt;1 Box gold and silver stud decorations &lt;br&gt;1 Box gold stud decorations &lt;br&gt;30 Rolls of striping tape &lt;br&gt;1 Pair precision tweezers\n				    	\n					&lt;/p&gt;\n        		\n        		\n        	\n        \n                \n        \n        \n      \n      \n    \n    \n\n     \n        ', 'https://www.amazon.com/dp/B073QGJBZB/', 'A TERRIFIC MULTI PART KIT FOR CREATING NAIL ART. Use this kit to create an infinite variety of your own dazzling nail-art designs with brushwork, studs, rhinestones, and more.<br />\nALL THE NAIL ART BRUSHES YOU\'LL EVER NEED. The 15 piece brush set includes flat fan brushes, line drawing brushes, dotting brushes, angled brushes, and much more.<br />\nA RANGE OF 3D DECORATIONS AND STRIPING TAPES. Also includes rhinestones in 12 colors, gold and silver stud appliques, and 30 different colors and widths of striping tapes. <br />\nA BEAUTIFUL PAIR OF PRECISION TWEEZERS. These tweezers have ground superfine angled tips. They\'re perfect for picking up and placing studs, rhinestones and tape.<br />\nNO RISK PURCHASE, FULL MONEY BACK GUARANTEE. If you\'re unsatisfied with this item for any reason, we\'ll immediately send you a replacement or refund your purchase price.<br />\n', 1542335122, 2, '', '', '', 1, 1, 1, NULL, NULL, 1, 1),
(116, 'ETEREAUTY Facial Brush Waterproof Body Facial Cleansing Brush for Deep Cleansing, Gentle Exfoliating and Removing Blackhead with 5 Brush Heads', 31, 0, 2228554, 100, 24.99, 24.99, 1, '423,424,425,426,427,428,429', '\n        \n\n\n\n\n\n  \n    \n  \n\n\n        \n        \n     \n	       \n     \n\n     \n                              \n     \n       	       \n        \n        &lt;!-- show up to 2 reviews by default --&gt; \n        \n        	\n        	\n        		\n        			&lt;p&gt;With the ETEREAUTY body and facial cleansing brush, enjoy beauty salon skin care&amp;nbsp;at home. &lt;br&gt;You can give yourself a full spa-quality skin-cleaning treatment any time you want. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;What can you achieve with face brush? &lt;br&gt; Minimizes pores &lt;br&gt; Removes blackheads &lt;br&gt; Intensive removal of dead skin cells &lt;br&gt; Helps skin tighten and remove wrinkles &lt;br&gt; Fresh complexion by stimulating blood circulation and metabolism &lt;br&gt;Improved skin appearance through gentle and porous cleansing, especially for removal of make-up. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Portable size: &lt;br&gt;The face cleansing brush&amp;nbsp;kit is small enough to take with you to the gym, to work, on vacation or business trips, so you can always be looking and feeling terrific. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Five attachments: &lt;br&gt; Crude polish accessory Crude polish accessory for ripping the tough skin and cutting off.. &lt;br&gt; Small short-bristle brush for gentle, thorough cleansing of pores. &lt;br&gt; Small long-bristle brush for more intense cleansing and mild exfoliating. &lt;br&gt; Pumice pad for gently removing calluses from elbows and feet. &lt;br&gt; Large brush for body, hands and feet. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Note： &lt;br&gt;Requires four AA batteries (not included).\n				    	\n					&lt;/p&gt;\n        		\n        		\n        	\n        \n                \n        \n        \n      \n      \n    \n    \n\n     \n        ', 'https://www.amazon.com/dp