ith ingrown hairs.\n        &lt;/p&gt;\n    \n\n    \n    \n        &lt;p class=&quot;a-spacing-base&quot;&gt;\n            And naturally, these tweezers can also be used for other purposes, such as removing splinters, holding and placing false eyelashes, and so on.\n        &lt;/p&gt;\n    \n\n    \n    \n        &lt;p class=&quot;a-spacing-base&quot;&gt;\n            Along with your tweezers, you\'ll receive a portable magnifying mirror with powerful 10X magnification and a suction cup mount so you can stick it to your regular mirror or elsewhere. &lt;span class=&quot;a-text-bold&quot;&gt;The best magnifying distance is within 13 cm, far distance will cause dizziness.&lt;/span&gt;\n        &lt;/p&gt;\n    \n\n    \n    \n        &lt;p class=&quot;a-spacing-base&quot;&gt;\n            For best results, plucking eyebrows should be done after showering, while the hairs are soft and follicles are open. Pull hairs in the direction of growth.\n        &lt;/p&gt;\n    \n\n    \n    \n        &lt;p class=&quot;a-spacing-base&quot;&gt;\n            Cosmetologists suggest you step back from your mirror every now and then to get an overall view of your face so you don\'t over-pluck.\n        &lt;/p&gt;\n    \n\n    \n    \n\n    \n    \n        &lt;p class=&quot;a-spacing-base&quot;&gt;\n            &lt;span class=&quot;a-text-bold&quot;&gt;Package includes:&lt;/span&gt;\n        &lt;/p&gt;\n    \n\n    \n    \n        &lt;p class=&quot;a-spacing-base&quot;&gt;\n            2x Slanted Flat Tip Tweezers\n        &lt;/p&gt;\n    \n\n    \n    \n        &lt;p class=&quot;a-spacing-base&quot;&gt;\n            1x Small Pointed Tip Tweezers\n        &lt;/p&gt;\n    \n\n    \n    \n        &lt;p class=&quot;a-spacing-base&quot;&gt;\n            1x Medium Pointed Tip Tweezers\n        &lt;/p&gt;\n    \n\n    \n    \n        &lt;p class=&quot;a-spacing-base&quot;&gt;\n            1x Carrying Case (Black)\n        &lt;/p&gt;\n    \n\n    \n    \n        &lt;p class=&quot;a-spacing-bas