licles are open.&lt;br&gt; Pull hairs in the direction of growth.&lt;br&gt; Cosmetologists recommend stepping back from your mirror periodically to get an overall view of your face so you don\'t over-pluck.&lt;br&gt; &lt;br&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;a-text-bold&quot;&gt;How to use:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt; Pull the skin between the hair follicle taut, not tight.&lt;br&gt; Tweeze hairs parallel to the direction of their growth (pull to the right on right-sided brows, the left on left-sided brows)&lt;br&gt; Pay attention to speed. Rapid movements equal less pain.&lt;br&gt; If you\'re sensitive to pain, ice the area after you\'ve removed all of the offending strands (hairs fall out easier with warm skin).\n        &lt;/p&gt;\n    \n\n\n\n&lt;/div&gt;\n\n                            \n                        \n                    \n                \n                \n            \n        &lt;/div&gt;\n    \n&lt;/div&gt;\n\n    \n\n\n\n                \n                \n            \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n    \n    \n    \n\n    \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\n\n\n    \n    \n\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\n\n        \n        \n        \n  \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n        \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n&lt;div id=&quot;legal_feature_div&quot; class=&quot;feature&quot; data-feature-name=&quot;legal&quot;&gt;\n         \n     \n\n\n\n\n    \n\n    \n    \n    \n        \n            \n                \n	                \n	                \n	                	\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n	                \n                \n            \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n    \n    \n    \n\n    \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    &lt;/div&gt;\n\n\n\n    \n    \n\n\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\n\n        \n        \n        \n  \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n        \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    \n    \n\n  \n    \n    \n\n\n    \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\