  The  blades are made from finest stainless steel, and the blades are covered  by plastic almost all the way up to the edge of the blade to provide  safe, controlled shaving. \n\n        &lt;/p&gt;\n    \n\n    \n    \n        &lt;p class=&quot;a-spacing-base&quot;&gt;\n            Each of the six razors has a protective cover for safety and to keep it sharp. \n\n        &lt;/p&gt;\n    \n\n    \n    \n        &lt;p class=&quot;a-spacing-base&quot;&gt;\n            &lt;span class=&quot;a-text-bold&quot;&gt;To use these razors, first comb your brows so the hair is all in line.&lt;/span&gt; \n\n        &lt;/p&gt;\n    \n\n    \n    \n        &lt;p class=&quot;a-spacing-base&quot;&gt;\n            Many  women like to define their brows with eyebrow powder or pencil before  using their eyebrow razor, darkening the ideal shape of their brows  before removing the hairs that fall outside that shape. \n\n        &lt;/p&gt;\n    \n\n    \n    \n        &lt;p class=&quot;a-spacing-base&quot;&gt;\n            To shave, hold the razor at a 45° angle to your skin and use a very light touch. \n\n        &lt;/p&gt;\n    \n\n    \n    \n        &lt;p class=&quot;a-spacing-base&quot;&gt;\n            You may want to apply a skin moisturizer to the eyebrow area before shaving to soften the hairs. \n\n        &lt;/p&gt;\n    \n\n    \n    \n        &lt;p class=&quot;a-spacing-base&quot;&gt;\n            You can find lots of videos and articles about using eyebrow razors on the web. \n\n        &lt;/p&gt;\n    \n\n    \n    \n        &lt;p class=&quot;a-spacing-base&quot;&gt;\n            Not  just for eyebrows, these razors can also be used to remove fine hair  elsewhere on your face, which helps makeup go on more smoothly to give  you a perfectly groomed look. \n\n        &lt;/p&gt;\n    \n\n    \n    \n        &lt;p class=&quot;a-spacing-base&quot;&gt;\n            They can also be used to remove stray hairs around the bikini area.  \n        &lt;/p&gt;\n    \n\n\n\n&lt;/div&gt;\n\