(103, 'Ladies Electric Shaver, ETEREAUTY Women Electric Razor Bikini Trimmer Body Hair Removal 4 in 1 Painless Cordless Use Wet or Dry', 36, 0, 2186403, 100, 29.99, 29.99, 1, '404', '\n        \n\n\n\n\n\n  \n    \n  \n\n\n        \n        \n     \n	       \n     \n\n     \n                              \n     \n       	       \n        \n        &lt;!-- show up to 2 reviews by default --&gt; \n        \n        	\n        	\n        		\n        			&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;In this one elegant electric razor you can take care of a host of personal grooming needs. &lt;/b&gt; &lt;br&gt;Four different heads pop on and off the power unit: A 3 in 1 general shaver, best for shaving your legs; a smaller precision shaver, good for following the curves under your arms or shaving your bikini area; a precision trimmer for sideburns or shaping your bikini line, and a facial cleansing brush for gentle and thorough spa-quality skin cleansing. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;The power electric shaver and heads are all waterproof and fully immersible.&lt;/b&gt; &lt;br&gt;So you can choose either the quick convenience of a dry shave or the comfort and luxury of using the shaver in the bath or shower with your favorite shaving foam or gel. &lt;br&gt;And of course, being fully immersible makes it easy to clean this item under the tap after use. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;If you\'ve never used a powered facial cleansing brush before, you\'re in for a treat. &lt;/b&gt; &lt;br&gt;The fine, soft bristles of the cleansing brush give you a gentle but deep pore-cleaning and exfoliating wash, leaving your skin feeling fresh and invigorated. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;You get all of this in one hand-friendly electric shaver that\'s great to look at as well as easy and pleasant to use. &lt;/b&gt; &lt;br&gt;It\'s conveniently rechargeable as well, so there are no batteries to replace. Order today and bring your body and facial grooming to a new level! &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Package includes:&lt;